Package proguard.classfile.editor

Class VariableRemapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • proguard.classfile.editor.VariableRemapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LocalVariableTargetElementVisitor, TargetInfoVisitor, TypeAnnotationVisitor, AttributeVisitor, LocalVariableInfoVisitor, LocalVariableTypeInfoVisitor, InstructionVisitor
    public class VariableRemapper
extends java.lang.Object
implements AttributeVisitor, InstructionVisitor, LocalVariableInfoVisitor, LocalVariableTypeInfoVisitor, TypeAnnotationVisitor, TargetInfoVisitor, LocalVariableTargetElementVisitor
    This AttributeVisitor remaps variable indexes in all attributes that it visits, based on a given index map.
